The paper discusses the optimization mystery of deep learning, which is a core topic in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
